{"tid":2367132,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"億萬男富豪愛上女兒前男友！求婚成功得意預告：代孕將生下女寶寶","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T09:04:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f56cd1ed62692babf6da0ae54fdd5b81d661731","tid":2367132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1792486&amp;from=m.facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1792486%26from%3Dm.facebook.com&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=70513c8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1792486&amp;from=m.facebook.com</a>"},{"pid":"86d3d29a6d39c98862cd75a9002959894ec973c4","tid":2367132,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"50歲的億萬富豪巴洛（Barrie Drewitt-Barlow）去年和結婚超過20年的伴侶東尼（Tony）離婚，並和女兒的前男友斯考特（Scott Hutchinson）相戀，他日前發出和斯考特求婚的影片，預告10月28日代理孕母將替他們生下一名女嬰。<br />\n<br />\n根據《太陽報》報導，巴洛和東尼1999年透過代理孕母產下雙胞胎，被稱為「英國首位同性戀父親」，但巴洛在和斯考特相識後，發現他才是自己的真愛，毅然決然和東尼離婚，並在近日全家到克羅埃西亞度假時，向斯考特求婚成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴洛把求婚安排在赫瓦爾島，他在船上灑滿玫瑰花瓣，布置蠟燭、美酒和鮮花，並準備一顆超大的鑽戒，他21日在ig上發出現場影片，並預告10月28日代理孕母將生下一名女嬰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴洛和斯考特的婚事得到前夫及女兒薩弗隆（Saffron）的祝福，「我很高興又一次當了父親，儘管此事也代表我和托尼多年的婚姻正式結束，但他仍興奮地表示祝福」。薩弗隆也說，「只要他們開心，我就不會打擾。」<br />\n<br />\n巴洛目前除了包括薩弗隆在內的雙胞胎女兒外，還有3名小孩，而托尼目前仍住在巴里價值600萬英鎊（約2.4億元台幣）的豪宅中，還將在寶寶出生後做他的教父。"},{"pid":"bb641ccae943968163b6b01c5f34e66dad5782eb","tid":2367132,"uid":208935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"下半世唔洗做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b710e8491f2c8476d1bf1c033ac24596213ba08d","tid":2367132,"uid":170249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"佢屌過佢個女個閪 <br />\n但條女個老豆又屌過佢菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211ddc77b41935720ebf3b9ac719724730efbfd8","tid":2367132,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b710e8491f2c8476d1bf1c033ac24596213ba08d","tid":2367132,"uid":170249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"佢屌過佢個女個閪 <br />\n但條女個老豆又屌過佢菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"串燒"},{"pid":"356a2883295d50fcaaaae68bb786c279ca8980dd","tid":2367132,"uid":116960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b710e8491f2c8476d1bf1c033ac24596213ba08d","tid":2367132,"uid":170249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"佢屌過佢個女個閪 <br />\n但條女個老豆又屌過佢菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"你唔比個老豆做0?"},{"pid":"2dcb05ea9900e4c142a938cc0c26abd10d5a1247","tid":2367132,"uid":165213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b710e8491f2c8476d1bf1c033ac24596213ba08d","tid":2367132,"uid":170249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"佢屌過佢個女個閪 <br />\n但條女個老豆又屌過佢菊花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"然後同佢講 邊個屌我個女就要屌返佢菊花"},{"pid":"0225a4bc1b0f6963c245a89630dc3a946276cc5e","tid":2367132,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"佢個女唔係佢親生?"},{"pid":"7d7ac1ce529959637c3bc16d4728f70e254f8019","tid":2367132,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dcb05ea9900e4c142a938cc0c26abd10d5a1247","tid":2367132,"uid":165213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b710e8491f2c8476d1bf1c033ac24596213ba08d","tid":2367132,"uid":170249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"佢屌過佢個女個閪 <br />\n但條女個老豆又屌過佢菊花<i